cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with video frame inpainting, which involves filling in missing frames in a video sequence. This task is related to computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM), as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) due to the use of deep learning techniques. Additionally, the paper involves temporal modeling and prediction, which is relevant to graphics (cs.GR).
